        "action": "Review the safety of electric buses",
        "additional_details": "We feel it's time for the Government to investigate the causes of all electric bus fires and introduce any necessary measures to prevent them.\r\n \r\nAs bus companies use more and more electric vehicles we need to be confident that they are as safe as possible.",
